nodes.text: This slicer recovered an image for Jedi Padawan Ferren Barr from the backup archive of a Coruscant Security Force holocam stationed above the temple district on the night that Anakin Skywalker attacked the Jedi Temple.
The slicer was first mentioned, albeit unnamed, in the canon comic Darth Vader: Dark Lord of the Sith 14 written by Charles Soule and pencilled by Giuseppe Camuncoli.
